### Device Event - VPN connected
POST http://localhost:8080/device-event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deviceId": "abc123def456ghi789",
  "eventType": "VPN_CONNECTED",
  "payload": {
    "server": "us-east-1",
    "protocol": "wireguard",
    "latency_ms": 45
  }
}

### Device Event - VPN disconnected
POST http://localhost:8080/device-event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deviceId": "abc123def456ghi789",
  "eventType": "VPN_DISCONNECTED",
  "payload": {
    "server": "us-east-1",
    "duration_seconds": 3600,
    "bytes_transferred": 1048576
  }
}

### Device Event - App crash
POST http://localhost:8080/device-event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deviceId": "abc123def456ghi789",
  "eventType": "APP_CRASH",
  "payload": {
    "error": "OutOfMemoryError",
    "stack": "java.lang.OutOfMemoryError..."
  }
}

### Device Event - Missing deviceId
POST http://localhost:8080/device-event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventType": "VPN_CONNECTED"
}
